      <p>Each new edition adds words that have entered mainstream English usage. Recent additions include technology terms, cultural words from world Englishes, and scientific vocabulary that has crossed into common use. Occasionally, words are also removed — typically archaic terms that no longer appear in any modern dictionary.</p>

